{"tid":381410,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"情侶只要開始同居, 愛情就會加快變成親情","createTime":"2017-08-31T02:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T00:18:23.000Z","uid":139262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0ad5c7f2a8ec7a01f9538f31e41be69cb257127","tid":381410,"uid":139262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:21:21.000Z","msg":"幾個男人 friend (有伴侶) 覺得源於男人大多數都係貪新鮮, 同居左, 朝晚見住 (唔計返工), 好快就會變得唔新鮮<br />\n<br />\n各位有無保鮮方法<br />\n<br />\n利申: 已結婚男 (無得唔同居)"},{"pid":"ac1ba178c55ee68ab783a4f76714e2315131757c","tid":381410,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾個男人 friend (有伴侶) 覺得源於男人大多數都係貪新鮮, 同居左, 朝晚見住 (唔計返工), 好快就會變得唔新鮮<br />\n<br />\n各位有無保鮮方法<br />\n<br />\n利申: 已結婚男 (無得唔同居)</blockquote><br />\n因為同居左有時會少左出街，覺得朝見晚見其實都唔洗出街，keep住每個weekend都去做啲特別嘢，自然會keep得住"},{"pid":"474a6ed55563fcedc6c729ac0da997db439f8d0d","tid":381410,"uid":139262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:30:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n因為同居左有時會少左出街，覺得朝見晚見其實都唔洗出街，keep住每個weekend都去做啲特別嘢，自然會keep得住</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔係話 keep 唔住, 已經盡量 weekend 搵野搞, 只係覺得少左果種感覺.  我覺得我老婆覺得我地關係依然係愛情, 但我就少左, 有咩可以令我增加返<br />\n<br />\n我又唔想為左咁樣而生小朋友"},{"pid":"bd9f00187314c25c17c9e193e231f0de0f6c2d1a","tid":381410,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:48:26.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n非常懷念以前一個人住既日子"},{"pid":"40fa0a3987a0765a65033cdc1107fad31de9ad99","tid":381410,"uid":139262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:52:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n非常懷念以前一個人住既日子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實最好係一星期有3-4日自己住, 但現實係無可能"},{"pid":"077ba8dc4e2a00d65b4543eee5da9defc2753343","tid":381410,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T03:22:38.000Z","msg":"愛情係火花<br />\n<br />\n幾耐既愛情,都會變親情,<br />\n<br />\n睇開d啦"},{"pid":"d10f432497d70c0fcf117836d56a08d70ba1b20d","tid":381410,"uid":137089,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T03:26:58.000Z","msg":"愛情去到最後就係兩個個體赤裸裸地一齊生活<br />\n<br />\n好多厭倦之後好多麻木 但依然會不時係某一件小事上 覺得：「呀有呢個人係身邊好好。」<br />\n<br />\n然後靠呢d小事行落去"},{"pid":"aea63446fe93c561ddc4072151015ff4607cedc5","tid":381410,"uid":139262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T03:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愛情係火花<br />\n<br />\n幾耐既愛情,都會變親情,<br />\n<br />\n睇開d啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時間到 d 6 ~70歲甚至更大 d 兩公婆重好鬼恩愛咁覺得好勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8b7f28ca2fc28aa1d6a64526b89bb9bcd8415e","tid":381410,"uid":139262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T03:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時<span style=\"color: red;\">見</span>到 d 6 ~70歲甚至更大 d 兩公婆重好鬼恩愛咁覺得好勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2d19029afaeff3e85e02b2dbddb2408ae9bea251","tid":381410,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T03:36:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c43f0b4ceb62176ef0569864503a8f49b36a7c","tid":381410,"uid":139262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T03:44:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n方便左, 係我同意, 但你覺得同未同居之前對對方果種熱情有無淡到?"},{"pid":"b40b7812bc11c9746b71bffa91dbd2a54c99454e","tid":381410,"uid":7886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:18:23.000Z","msg":"愛情呢啲係火花，會有磨完嘅一日<br />\n一齊住嘅話，點都好，一定要做啲嘢keep住呢個感覺"}]}